  <h2 id="-overview" style="margin-top: 0;">ðŸ“Œ Overview</h2>
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #c9d1d9; line-height: 1.6;">
    This repository contains Python + Selenium automation training work completed during the Wipro training program.
    It includes daily practice folders, revision notes, and case study questions. The goal is to build strong fundamentals,
    write clean automation scripts, and follow testing best practices.
  </p>
</div>

