<div style="padding: 18px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #30363d; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);">
  <h2 id="-getting-started" style="margin-top:0;">ðŸš€ Getting Started</h2>

  <h3 style="margin-bottom: 6px;">Prerequisites</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Python 3.8+</li>
    <li>pip</li>
    <li>Google Chrome / Firefox</li>
    <li>ChromeDriver / GeckoDriver (match browser version)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 style="margin-bottom: 6px;">Setup</h3>

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/WiproTraining.git

# Go to project folder
cd WiproTraining

# Install Selenium
pip install selenium
